    <item>
      <title>马克龙称即使工党输掉法国大选他也不会辞职</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-12/macron-won-t-quit-if-his-party-is-defeated-in-french-election</link>
      <description><![CDATA[法国总统埃马纽埃尔·马克龙表示，如果他的政党在提前举行的议会选举中成绩不佳，他不会辞职，并呼吁选民不要屈服于“极端主义的狂热”。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-12/macron-won-t-quit-if-his-party-is-defeated-in-french-election</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 12 Jun 2024 10:17:18 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>欧盟将对中国进口电动汽车征收最高 48% 的关税</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-12/eu-to-impose-additional-tariffs-on-ev-imports-from-china</link>
      <description><![CDATA[欧盟将从下个月开始对从中国出口的电动汽车征收额外关税，税率最高可达 48%，此举将进一步加剧贸易紧张局势，并增加购买电动汽车的成本。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-12/eu-to-impose-additional-tariffs-on-ev-imports-from-china</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 12 Jun 2024 09:47:15 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
